Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: Wyoming has 5 more cryptocoin-friendly laws proposed, some of which sound pretty interesting: https://twitter.com/CaitlinLong_/status/1069247321546940416

Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: One of the laws allow banks to give bank accounts to cryptocoin businesses, which is pretty important. Right now, it's a legal mess, at the federal/country level. So they are defining things at the state level, so banks can legally deal with cryptocoin companies, is the TLDR
